XML/Generator/RSS10/lgcl version 0.01
=====================================

This module extends Dave Rolsky's XML::Generator::RSS10 to
support categories taken from the UK Local Government Category
List (lgcl), a controlled vocabulary for use in the UK e-Government
Metadata Standard (egms).

The module is intended for use only with XML::Generator::RSS10::egms.
Please see the documentation accompanying that module for further
information.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires:

   XML::Generator::RSS10

It is intended for use only with:

   XML::Generator::RSS10::egms


